To Whom It May Concern:
This is to certify that Mr. A.B. Smith has been employed by this company for the past 6 years as a mason.
Signed,
Robert Johnson, President, Western Stone Co, Las Vegas
Note: Mr. Smith has been a valuable employee and we regret losing him.\nRJ
